description: A year after fire devastated Notre Dame, construction has stopped and the cathedral is quiet.
title: Notre Dame fire: Fragile old lady of Paris waits for rescue
title_page: Notre Dame fire: Fragile old lady of Paris waits for rescue - BBC News
maintext: "It's still fragile," he told me. "It just takes a storm, a tornado, and it will move. When the old scaffolding that is welded together is removed, then we can say the cathedral is 100% saved."
